Reaction 2: \ce{SiO2 + 6HF -> H2SiF6 + 2H2O}   ΔH₂ = \pu{-100.3 kJ mol^{-1}}
Reaction 3 (reversed and x6): \ce{6NaOH + 6HF -> 6H2O + 6NaF}   ΔH'₃ = \pu{-369 kJ mol^{-1}}
